reviewText: Amazing product with crisp visuals and clear sound. The product was delivered on time and without any apparent "rough handling" with the package internally/externally. If you are a Duck fan, I highly recommend this product.
This was a great game and I will continue to watch it over and over again, great win.  Go Ducks
Great blu ray DVD of my Oregon Ducks convincing Fiesta Bowl win over Kansas State Wildcats! Go Ducks!! Win the Day!!
